<plot>An exciting and thoroughly gripping short thriller which finds three men waiting for another; the enigmatic O'Brien; all strangers to each other and all waiting for very different reasons. Their motives are gradually revealed and the story's conclusion, which appears ambiguous at first but actually perfectly wraps up everything satisfyingly, is a masterstroke.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?645959</url></doc>
